OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FXL bully dogs will not be  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbanned in NI - minister    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, XL bully dogs will not be banned in NI 
OL,6, under new plans to restrict their      
OL,7, ownership, Andrew Muir has said.       
OL,9,FIt will remain legal to own one of the 
OL,10,Fdogs but they must be muzzled and on a 
OL,11,Flead in public.                        
OL,13,FThe agriculture and rural affairs      
OL,14,Fminister also said a new scheme will be
OL,15,Fset up requiring owners to register    
OL,16,Ftheir dog with the authorities.        
OL,18,FThe breed has already been banned in   
OL,19,FEngland and Wales. Scotland introduced 
OL,20,Fsimilar laws last month.               
